Insider Activity


Individual




Barb Jean Samardzich



Ms. Barb J. Samardzich is on the Board of Directors at Adient plc and MTS Systems Corp. Ms. Samardzich was previously employed as Non-Executive Director by Ford Otomotiv Sanayi AS, Chief Operating Officer & Vice President by Ford of Europe, Inc., and Vice President-Global Product Programs by Ford Motor Co. She received her undergraduate degree from the University of Florida, a graduate degree from Carnegie Mellon University and a graduate degree from Wayne State University (Michigan).



